---
title: Mumbai Beef & Potato Curry with Garlic Rice & Roasted Peanuts
description: This creamy Indian coconut beef curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with
bright veggies, hearty chunks of potato and finished with a sprinkling of flair from the roasted peanuts.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mumbai-beef-potato-curry-7c08b9f8.jpg
